data.description:
Welcome to your ideal home or investment property! This "turn key", newly remodeled cash flowing rental home offers 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and a wealth of modern upgrades. Step inside to find a beautifully renovated interior boasting new paint, carpet, and flooring that perfectly complement the elegant design. 

The heart of the home, the remodeled kitchen, features new stainless steel appliances and updated fixtures, making it an ideal space for culinary adventures and entertaining. Additionally, enjoy the convenience of a finished attic space and basement, perfect for additional living space area.

Outside, revel in the spacious front porch—a great spot for morning coffees or evening relaxation. This property also includes a two-car garage, providing ample parking and storage space.

Located in Cleveland Heights, this home seamlessly blends modern amenities with timeless charm. Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautifully updated property your new home or investment!
